{"tid":1068068,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭月娥：若7月前無法律處理台灣殺人案公義不能彰顯","createTime":"2019-03-19T03:38:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-19T08:05:49.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":40,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"71d73843b555adee09d9ed6d51652937875e8e26","tid":1068068,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T03:38:42.000Z","msg":"行政長官林鄭月娥重申，政府建議修訂《逃犯條例》及相關條例，目的是希望完善目前機制，以維護公義及確保公共安全。她強調，事件有一定時間性，因為涉及一宗台灣殺人案，現時本港法例及安排不能處理，如果在今年7月前未能找到法律可行方法處理，便出現家屬或立法會議員不願見的情況，即公義不能彰顯。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥出席行政會議前說，政府聽到很多關注，保安局局長李家超每日馬不停蹄，與商界及其他界別解釋，條例對人權及程序都有很多保障，希望可釋除疑慮，經諮詢及聽取意見後，政府會否對條例草案作改變或細化，要留待李家超處理。"},{"pid":"784059fa73eda3e127f48855ff58ecf22aefdf1d","tid":1068068,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T03:38:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1448426-20190319.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1448426-20190319.htm&d=pHv7ulxaPAPTUdGhwq1YMUxj1a1M9JfR6d2dSWReNkw%3D&h=bb35f8ad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1448426-20190319.htm&h=0c2f2325\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1448426-20190319.htm</a>"},{"pid":"fa5c1ae8918ed38644a201671ce7b604e8d414e5","tid":1068068,"uid":164050,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T03:41:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8697404c6b82cab5154d65297cde3ee8c4db1d23","tid":1068068,"uid":130695,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T03:43:45.000Z","msg":"香港仲有人權?"},{"pid":"89bb0fe1179b7fa3d1eace8a4c96859828f545e2","tid":1068068,"uid":76310,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T03:46:59.000Z","msg":"痴那線<br />\n一個無公義既正苦利用追求公義來實行不公義"},{"pid":"278a44567d87dad82e5e02fc99a452e6a7cfc44e","tid":1068068,"uid":4285,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19